{"tid":1569002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被揭曾赴美生子　「央視一姐」董卿大談愛國惹惡評　網民：太虛偽","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T12:55:48.000Z","uid":56533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f888b649bd7fefdacc5226bd3c652c8ad152f53d","tid":1569002,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d73a4152e39591811a8b339.png/djHWhPeZNnQTXV4KvyxxTZ0aJ7vyFFufGswWDRrMFg0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d73a4152e39591811a8b339.png%2FdjHWhPeZNnQTXV4KvyxxTZ0aJ7vyFFufGswWDRrMFg0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=678bd795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，被稱為「央視一姐」的女主持董卿在電視節目《開學第一課》中教育學生要愛國和愛護五星紅旗。惟此番「正能量」言論卻意外惹來大批內地網民的惡評。有人揭發董卿曾赴美產子，<span style=\"color: red;\">讓兒子成為了美國人，自己卻在中國教育孩子要熱愛祖國</span>，做法十分虛偽和矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，央視製作的《開學第一課》是面對內地中小學生的電視專題節目，於每年秋季開學日（9月1日）前後播放，節目的內容選取具「正能量」的人物及事件，以此對學生進行教育，特別是進行愛國主義、民族主義教育。<br />\n<br />\n董卿近日在主持該節目時，在台上教育學生說：「特殊的五星紅旗，曾經是多少人活下去的希望，也曾經是多少人內心最崇高的信仰和榮耀，我們今天再次和同學們來講述這個故事，就是希望大家要明白一個道理，今天的我們要像愛護生命一樣愛護五星旗，因為國旗神聖不可侵犯。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d73ad140062511817a9a0ce.png/X8dF_0fqICL9zB18j66Ut8eY5tN3Sp0O0jINYdIyDWE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d73ad140062511817a9a0ce.png%2FX8dF_0fqICL9zB18j66Ut8eY5tN3Sp0O0jINYdIyDWE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2737e223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但節目播出後沒多久，董卿的言論卻引起了網民的嘲諷和抵制。有人說，「最討厭這種人，口是心非。」還有人直言，「董卿的孩子是美國籍，自己卻打著為人師表的幌子，站在央視大舞台，教育著中國的孩子們，教育他們愛國，還大談民族精神和崇高信仰 ，這是多麼的滑稽可笑。」此外，有人甚至質問，「請你們央視別再拿這種假愛國來欺騙我們百姓，我們百姓愛國才是真的！你們回答一下有幾個孩子是中國籍？」<br />\n<br />\n據內媒報道，董卿面對質疑，曾自辯孩子是美國籍，為的是能讓孩子接受到更好的教育，並不影響她自己愛國。惟網民的怒氣難平，紛紛留言稱「不知道她愛的是哪個國」，也有網民認為「國籍就是立場，沒啥好說的」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，也有少數網民為董卿辯護，「怎麼就不能談愛國了。照這個邏輯，華人華僑也不能談愛國了唄。」「愛國心不是在中國就叫愛國，是無論在哪都記得自己的根自己的魂。董卿主持了那麼多節目，讓更多的外國人認識到中國人的美和中國的文化，這就是愛國。」<br />\n<br />\n據悉，董卿從2005年開始主持央視春節聯歡晚會。2014年，41歲的董卿突然在央視幕前消失，赴美深造，隨後就傳出其在加州產下一子。後來董卿說：「到了一定的年紀，許多事情也不能被推遲，否則將永遠失去這種機會。」之後在一次發布會中，董卿首次承認自己有個兒子。"},{"pid":"6a1213e29370fd1775098d72633d8b5b4675b605","tid":1569002,"uid":30966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:46:09.000Z","msg":"生意黎姐"},{"pid":"96535c9f33caaa9651741294d2678614563a45e0","tid":1569002,"uid":210638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:47:15.000Z","msg":"反美是工作，愛美是生活<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"2f24377b380ee6a0b174d848fa51a09826375533","tid":1569002,"uid":135067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣"},{"pid":"e74efebf7aa775d1188ca6a9fd0e275989915165","tid":1569002,"uid":22832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"怎麼就不能談愛國了。照這個邏輯，華人華僑也不能談愛國了唄。<br />\n<br />\n咁愛國就咪撚做外國人"},{"pid":"d24f68060e82296dc0aebe77f00b082dd4d93e7f","tid":1569002,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"建議928死線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eaGoiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eaGoiS</a>"},{"pid":"3df8683c1d7bfa5a036164a297c80e41869948f2","tid":1569002,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"曾自辯孩子是美國籍，為的是能讓孩子接受到更好的教育<br />\n<br />\n即係嘲笑中国教育唔及美國啦"},{"pid":"f3ecd8b810adfd8fa3d6753a2166bb064e357a54","tid":1569002,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e74efebf7aa775d1188ca6a9fd0e275989915165","tid":1569002,"uid":22832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"怎麼就不能談愛國了。照這個邏輯，華人華僑也不能談愛國了唄。<br />\n<br />\n咁愛國就咪撚做外國人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"可以講愛佢移咗民去嘅國家<br />\n但係唔可以講愛中國,除非佢移民係想出去